  <summary date="2023-01-24T14:27:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Price Gouging Prevention Act of 2022 

This bill generally makes it unlawful to sell or offer for sale a good or service at an unconscionably excessive price during an exceptional market shock.

The bill also provides additional funding to the Federal Trade Commission.</summary>
